#month-banner("One", "Eight", "Tarot as Alchemical Mirror & Introduction to the Qabalah", "The symbolic skeleton of the Great Work — Mapping consciousness")

#v(0.8em)

#hm-note[
  Month 8 introduces the most complex symbolic framework of the curriculum: the
  Holy Qabalah and the Tree of Life. Do not expect students to grasp this fully
  in one month. The goal is imprinting and familiarity. The Tree of Life should
  be presented as a *living filing system* for their alchemical experiences. The
  Tarot practice shifts from keywords to pathwork, using the images as doorways
  to specific bands of consciousness. Ensure students maintain their Tarot
  journal as a primary document.
]

